We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

snippet.title: MUTTON BIRYANI | 3 FULL GOAT ROASTED MUTTON BIRYANI Recipe Cooking in Village | Arabian Biryani
snippet.description: Today in our village, we cooked a grand Arabian-style mutton biryani using three full goats. First, we boiled the whole goats in a large vessel with spices to make the meat tender and flavorful. Then, we carefully roasted each goat on a large tawa over a direct flame of firewood, adding a smoky, rich layer of flavor. After roasting, we layered the juicy mutton with aromatic basmati rice, hand-ground masalas, and traditional spices. This massive biryani was slow-cooked to perfection and shared during a village feast. A perfect blend of smoky, spicy, and tender mutton biryani with an Arabian touch.

de-DE.title: Lamm-Biryani | Rezept für 3 VOLLE, vom Ziegenbock geröstete Lamm-Biryani, Kochen im Dorf | Arabis...
de-DE.description: Heute haben wir in unserem Dorf ein großartiges Hammel-Biryani nach arabischer Art mit drei ganzen Ziegen zubereitet. Zuerst kochten wir die ganzen Ziegen in einem großen Gefäß mit Gewürzen, um das Fleisch zart und aromatisch zu machen. Anschließend rösteten wir jede Ziege vorsichtig auf einer großen Tawa über direkter Holzflamme, um ihr ein rauchiges, reichhaltiges Aroma zu verleihen. Nach dem Rösten schichteten wir das saftige Hammelfleisch mit aromatischem Basmatireis, handgemahlenen Masalas und traditionellen Gewürzen. Dieses riesige Biryani wurde langsam perfekt gegart und bei einem Dorffestmahl geteilt. Eine perfekte Mischung aus rauchigem, würzigem und zartem Hammel-Biryani mit arabischer Note.

id.title: Biryani Daging Kambing | 3 Resep Biryani Daging Kambing Panggang Utuh | Masakan Desa | Biryani Arab
id.description: Hari ini di desa kami, kami memasak biryani daging kambing ala Arab yang megah menggunakan tiga ekor kambing utuh. Pertama, kami merebus seluruh kambing dalam wadah besar berisi bumbu agar dagingnya empuk dan beraroma. Kemudian, kami memanggang setiap kambing dengan hati-hati di atas tawa besar di atas api kayu bakar langsung, menambahkan lapisan rasa berasap yang kaya. Setelah dipanggang, kami melapisi daging kambing yang empuk dengan nasi basmati yang harum, bumbu masala giling tangan, dan rempah-rempah tradisional. Biryani besar ini dimasak perlahan hingga sempurna dan dinikmati bersama dalam pesta desa. Perpaduan sempurna biryani daging kambing berasap, pedas, dan empuk dengan sentuhan Arab.

fr-FR.title: Biryani de mouton | Recette de 3 biryanis de mouton rôtis au chèvre entier | Biryani arabe
fr-FR.description: Aujourd'hui, dans notre village, nous avons cuisiné un grand biryani de mouton à l'arabe avec trois chèvres entières. Nous avons d'abord fait bouillir les chèvres entières dans un grand récipient avec des épices pour rendre la viande tendre et savoureuse. Ensuite, nous avons soigneusement rôti chaque chèvre sur un grand tawa, au-dessus d'une flamme de bois directe, ajoutant une riche saveur fumée. Après la cuisson, nous avons garni le mouton juteux de riz basmati aromatique, de masalas moulus à la main et d'épices traditionnelles. Ce biryani massif a été mijoté à la perfection et partagé lors d'un festin de village. Un mélange parfait de biryani de mouton fumé, épicé et tendre, avec une touche arabe.

ja.title: マトンビリヤニ | 3 ヤギ丸ごとローストしたマトンビリヤニのレシピ 村で調理 | アラビアンビリヤニ
ja.description: 今日、私たちの村では、ヤギ3頭を使った豪華なアラビア風マトンビリヤニを作りました。まず、ヤギを丸ごと大きな鍋でスパイスと一緒に煮込み、肉を柔らかく風味豊かに仕上げました。次に、大きなタワ（炙り鍋）に山羊を一頭ずつ入れ、薪の直火で丁寧に焼き上げ、スモーキーで豊かな風味を加えました。焼き上がった後、ジューシーなマトンに香り高いバスマティライス、手挽きのマサラ、そして伝統的なスパイスを重ねました。このボリュームたっぷりのビリヤニは、じっくりと時間をかけて完璧に調理され、村の宴会で皆でシェアしました。スモーキーでスパイシー、そして柔らかいマトンビリヤニにアラビア風の風味が絶妙に溶け合いました。

it.title: BIRYANI DI MONTONE | 3 Ricette COMPLETE PER BIRYANI DI MONTONE ARROSTO DI CAPRA Cucinare in un vi...
it.description: Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo cucinato un grandioso biryani di montone in stile arabo usando tre capre intere. Per prima cosa, abbiamo bollito le capre intere in un grande recipiente con spezie per rendere la carne tenera e saporita. Poi, abbiamo arrostito con cura ogni capretto su una grande tawa a fuoco diretto di legna da ardere, aggiungendo uno strato affumicato e ricco di sapore. Dopo la cottura, abbiamo guarnito il succoso montone con riso basmati aromatico, masala macinati a mano e spezie tradizionali. Questo enorme biryani è stato cotto lentamente alla perfezione e condiviso durante una festa di villaggio. Un perfetto mix di biryani di montone affumicato, piccante e tenero, con un tocco arabo.

es-US.title: BIRYANI DE CORDERO | 3 BIRYANI DE CORDERO ASADO DE CABRA COMPLETO Receta de cocina de pueblo | Bi...
es-US.description: Hoy en nuestro pueblo, cocinamos un magnífico biryani de cordero al estilo árabe con tres cabras enteras. Primero, hervimos las cabras enteras en una olla grande con especias para que la carne quedara tierna y sabrosa. Después, asamos cuidadosamente cada cabra en una tawa grande sobre una llama directa de leña, añadiendo una capa de sabor ahumado y rico. Después de asar, cubrimos el jugoso cordero con arroz basmati aromático, masalas molidas a mano y especias tradicionales. Este enorme biryani se cocinó a fuego lento a la perfección y se compartió durante un festín del pueblo. Una combinación perfecta de biryani de cordero ahumado, picante y tierno con un toque árabe.

nl-NL.title: Lamsvlees biryani | Recept voor 3 hele geroosterde geitenlamsvlees biryani | Arabische biryani
nl-NL.description: Vandaag kookten we in ons dorp een geweldige Arabische schapenbiryani met drie hele geiten. Eerst kookten we de hele geiten in een grote pan met kruiden om het vlees mals en smaakvol te maken. Vervolgens braadden we elke geit zorgvuldig op een grote tawa boven een open vuur, wat een rokerige, rijke smaak toevoegde. Na het braden legden we het sappige schapenvlees in laagjes met aromatische basmatirijst, handgemalen masala's en traditionele kruiden. Deze enorme biryani was perfect gegaard en werd gedeeld tijdens een dorpsfeest. Een perfecte mix van rokerige, pittige en malse schapenbiryani met een Arabisch tintje.

pl.title: MUTTON BIRYANI | 3 CAŁKOWITE PIECZONE MIĘSO KOZY MUTTON BIRYANI Przepis Gotowanie w wiosce | Arab...
pl.description: Dzisiaj w naszej wiosce ugotowaliśmy wspaniałe biryani z baraniny w stylu arabskim, używając trzech całych kóz. Najpierw ugotowaliśmy całe kozy w dużym naczyniu z przyprawami, aby mięso było delikatne i aromatyczne. Następnie ostrożnie upiekliśmy każdą kozę na dużym tawa nad bezpośrednim płomieniem drewna opałowego, dodając wędzoną, bogatą warstwę smaku. Po upieczeniu ułożyliśmy soczystą baraninę z aromatycznym ryżem basmati, ręcznie mielonymi masalami i tradycyjnymi przyprawami. To ogromne biryani zostało powoli ugotowane do perfekcji i podzielone podczas wiejskiej uczty. Idealne połączenie wędzonych, pikantnych i delikatnych biryani z baraniną z arabskim akcentem.

hi.title: मटन बिरयानी | 3 बकरे की भुनी हुई मटन बिरयानी रेसिपी | गांव में खाना बनाना | अरेबियन बिरयानी
hi.description: आज हमारे गाँव में, हमने तीन पूरे बकरों का इस्तेमाल करके एक शानदार अरबी शैली की मटन बिरयानी पकाई। सबसे पहले, हमने पूरे बकरों को एक बड़े बर्तन में मसालों के साथ उबाला ताकि उनका मांस नर्म और स्वादिष्ट हो। फिर, हमने हर बकरे को एक बड़े तवे पर लकड़ी की सीधी आंच पर सावधानी से भूना, जिससे उसमें धुएँ जैसी, भरपूर स्वाद की परत चढ़ गई। भूनने के बाद, हमने रसीले मटन पर खुशबूदार बासमती चावल, हाथ से पिसे हुए मसाले और पारंपरिक मसालों की परतें चढ़ाईं। इस विशाल बिरयानी को धीमी आँच पर पूरी तरह पकाया गया और गाँव के एक भोज में बाँटा गया। धुएँदार, मसालेदार और कोमल मटन बिरयानी का एक बेहतरीन मिश्रण, जिसमें अरबी स्वाद भी है।

pt-BR.title: BIRYANI DE CARNEIRO | 3 BIRYANI DE CARNEIRO ASSADOS COM CABRA | Receita de Biryani Árabe
pt-BR.description: Hoje, em nossa aldeia, preparamos um grandioso biryani de carneiro ao estilo árabe, usando três cabras inteiras. Primeiro, cozinhamos as cabras inteiras em uma panela grande com especiarias para deixar a carne macia e saborosa. Em seguida, assamos cuidadosamente cada cabra em uma tawa grande sobre fogo direto de lenha, adicionando uma camada rica e defumada de sabor. Depois de assadas, cobrimos o suculento carneiro com arroz basmati aromático, masalas moídos à mão e especiarias tradicionais. Este enorme biryani foi cozido lentamente até a perfeição e compartilhado durante um banquete na aldeia. Uma mistura perfeita de biryani de carneiro defumado, picante e macio com um toque árabe.

ko.title: 양고기 비리아니 | 3가지 염소 구이 양고기 비리아니 레시피 (마을에서 요리) | 아라비아 비리아니
ko.description: 오늘 저희 마을에서는 통째로 된 염소 세 마리를 사용하여 아라비아식 양고기 비리아니를 만들었습니다. 먼저, 큰 냄비에 염소 한 마리를 통째로 넣고 양념을 넣어 부드럽고 풍미 있게 삶았습니다. 그런 다음, 큰 타와(tawa)에 염소 한 마리를 넣고 장작불에 직접 구워 훈제 향과 풍부한 풍미를 더했습니다. 구운 후, 육즙이 풍부한 양고기에 향긋한 바스마티 쌀, 손으로 갈은 마살라, 그리고 전통 향신료를 겹겹이 얹었습니다. 이 푸짐한 비리아니는 완벽하게 천천히 조리되어 마을 잔치에 함께 나눴습니다. 아라비아의 풍미가 더해진 훈제 향과 매콤함, 그리고 부드러운 양고기 비리아니의 완벽한 조화였습니다.

snippet.title: Morni Official Music Video | Darshan Raval | Divyansha K | Siddharth A B| Naushad Khan | Indie Music
snippet.description:
"Morni" keeps the beloved tradition alive! Every monsoon, Darshan Raval gifts his fans a rain-soaked melody, and this year is no different. Sung and composed by Darshan himself, with heartfelt lyrics by Siddharth A. Bhavsar and Darshan Raval, the song captures the innocence of two hearts setting out on a beautiful, unknown journey of love. With a music video that reflects the charm of first monsoon romance, Morni is a promise fulfilled, and a memory waiting to be made.

snippet.title: Gaane Gaane | গানে গানে | Dhumketu | Dev | Subhashree | Arijit Singh | Shreya Ghoshal | Anupam Roy
snippet.description:
শুনুন দেব-শুভশ্রী অভিনীত নতুন ছবি, ধুমকেতু থেকে অরিজিৎ সিং ও শ্রেয়া ঘোষালের কন্ঠে ও অনুপম রায়ের সঙ্গীত পরিচালনায় নতুন গান, "গানে গানে"

Get ready to be swept away by the magic of music with "Gaane Gaane", a heartwarming romantic track that blends soulful vocals with mesmerizing visuals. snippet.title: Alice in Borderland: Season 3 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
The survival action series "Alice in Borderland" became the most watched Japanese Netflix title by worldwide audiences.

Now, the "games" that took the world by storm begin once again.

In the previous season, Arisu (#KentoYamazaki) and Usagi (#TaoTsuchiya) cleared all of the games and returned to the real world. They have since gotten married and established a happy life together. Their memories of the borderland were erased, but they see glimpses of it in dreams and hallucinations. One day, Usagi, led by afterlife researcher Ryuji (#KentoKaku), suddenly vanishes. At the same time as Usagi's disappearance, Banda (#HayatoIsomura) hands Arisu the final card: the Joker.

The uncharted journey led by the mysterious Joker card is about to unfold...

Season 3 of the Netflix Series "Alice in Borderland" is set for worldwide release on Thursday, September 25, 2025, only on Netflix.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81682895

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Alice in Borderland: Season 3 | Official Teaser | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

As new deadly games return, Arisu, Usagi and new players must navigate even more daunting, adrenaline-fueled challenges.

The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. snippet.title: चना दाल दोसा फटाफट बनायें झटपट परोसें, कुरकुरा टेस्टी स्पेशल नाश्ता । Instant Chana Dal Dosa Recipe
snippet.description:
बिना पहले से दाल भिगोये, बिना फरमेंट किए बनने वाला स्पेशल ब्रेकफास्ट - चना दाल दोसा, Quick Chana Dal Dosa Recipe –No Fermenting, Healthy and Tasty Chana Dal Dosa

#breakfast #dosa #nashta 

Ingredients for Chana Dal Dosa
चावल - Rice - 1 cup
चना दाल - Chana dal - 1/2 cup (100 grams)
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1 no
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 inch
मेथी दान - Fenugreek seeds - 1/2 tsp
दही - Curd - 1/2 cup
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
बेकिंग सोडा - Baking soda - 1/4 tsp

For Aloo Stuffing
तेल - Oil - 1 tbsp
सरसों के दाने - Mustard seeds - 1/2 tsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/4 tsp
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 tsp, grated
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1/2 tsp, chopped
टमाटर - Tomato - 1 no, chopped
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
लाल मिर्च पाउडर - Red chilli powder - 1/2 tsp
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1 tsp
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
करी पत्ता - Curry leaves - 10-12 no
हींग - Asafoetida - 1/2 pinch
आलू - Potato (boiled) - 4 no (400 grams)
हरा धनिया - Coriander
For Paneer Stuffing
तेल - Oil - 1 tbsp
स्वीट कॉर्न - Sweet corn - 2 tbsp
शिमला मिर्च - Capsicum - 1/2 cup, chopped
टमाटर - Tomato - 1 no, chopped
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1/2 tsp, chopped
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 tsp, grated
पनीर - Cottage cheese - 1/2 cup (100 grams)
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
काली मिर्च - Black pepper - 1/4 cup, crushed
हरा धनिया - Coriander
For Chutney
चने - Chickpeas - 1/2 cup, roasted
नारियल - Coconut - 1 cup, grated
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1.5 no
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 inch
नींबू क रस - lemon juice - 1 tbsp
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
तेल - Oil - 1/2 tbsp
सरसों के दाने - Mustard seeds - 1/2 tsp
करी पत्ता - Curry leaves - 15-20 no
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 2 no
कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च - Kashmiri red chilli - 1/2 pinch

For the Best recipes on YouTube, log onto - 
http://www.youtube.com/@nishamadhulika


Find us on Facebook at - 
https://www.facebook.com/nishamadhulika

Visit my Hindi Website
http://nishamadhulika.com

snippet.title: Namit Malhotra's Ramayana: The Introduction | Nitesh Tiwari | Ranbir, Yash, Hans Zimmer & AR Rahman
snippet.description:
An outcome through a collaboration of some of the world’s best to ensure that Ramayana is presented with the greatest amount of Reverence and Respect. 

Welcome to the Beginning. 

Let’s celebrate the IMMORTAL story of Rama v/s Ravana. 

Our Truth. Our History.

Directed by Nitesh Tiwari, Produced by Namit Malhotra’s Prime Focus Studios and 8-time Oscar winning VFX studio DNEG in association with Yash’s Monster Mind Creations; Ramayana is being filmed for IMAX and will release worldwide: Part 1 on Diwali 2026 and Part 2 on Diwali 2027.

Namit Malhotra’s Ramayana

Starring:
Ranbir Kapoor as Rama
Yash as Ravana
Sai Pallavi as Sita
Ravie Dubey as Lakshman
Sunny Deol as Hanuman

Co-Produced by Yash
Written by Shridhar Raghavan
Directed by Nitesh Tiwari

Music by Hans Zimmer & AR Rahman
Lyrics by Kumar Vishwas

VFX by DNEG (8-time Academy Award winners)

Filmed for IMAX

Presented by Prime Focus Studios in association with Monster Mind Creations

snippet.title: கட்டுன பொண்டாட்டிய அடிகிறதுக்கா மூஞ்சில இவ்வளவு பெரிய மீச வச்சிருக்க | Samuthiram | Super Good Films
snippet.description:
💥 Watch Our New Upload: Samuthiram Movie Back-to-Back Scenes | Emotional Family Drama! 💥

Dive deep into the intense and emotional world of Samuthiram, a gripping Tamil family drama starring Sarathkumar, Murali, Manoj Bharathiraja, Kaveri, Abhirami, Sindhu Menon, and Manjula Vijayakumar. These back-to-back scenes bring to light strong values, raw emotions, and powerful confrontations that question injustice within a family.

💬 “Kattuna ponnattiya adikirathukka moonjila ivvalavu periya meesha vachirukka?”
("Did you grow such a big moustache just to hit your own wife?")

This bold and unforgettable dialogue reflects the emotional weight and moral strength carried by the characters. Watch as relationships are tested and truths are unveiled in this unforgettable classic!

🎬 Movie: Samuthiram
🎭 Cast: Sarathkumar, Murali, Manoj Bharathiraja, Kaveri, Abhirami, Sindhu Menon, Manjula Vijayakumar

snippet.title: A little Surprise! ❤️ Amrutha Suresh | Abhirami Suresh | Ag vlogs
snippet.description:
Amidst the mess, moving boxes, and home shifting chaos… we paused for something that truly mattered 🥹💗

It was our dear Rasika’s birthday, and though it was a busy day filled with cleaning and packing, we decided to surprise her with a small cake, a simple gift, and a whole lot of love. 🎂🎁🍛

Watch this unplanned, beautiful moment that reminded us how small gestures can mean the world.
This one’s for the hearts that work quietly behind the scenes 💕

snippet.title: What Real Growth Means – Girish Mathrubootham, Founder & Executive Chairman, Freshworks | Gobinath
snippet.description:
Enquiries:
talk2gobinath@gmail.com

#Gobinath #girishmathrubootham #freshworks #startup #india #podcast #saas #ai #artificialintelligence #business #thegobinathpodcast #careeradvice #techleadership 

Stay ahead with direct updates from Gobinath — interviews, insights, and powerful voices.
Join the official WhatsApp Channel today:
https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Vb5gNn82Jl8DSfwhUM3G

     “SaaS is Dead. AI is the New King.”
In this high-impact episode, Gobinath sits down with Girish Mathrubootham, one of India’s most admired tech leaders, to explore the rise of AI, the future of startups, and what it takes to stay relevant in a world that’s changing faster than ever.

From the early days of Freshworks to launching Freddy AI, from the AI disruption wave to solving real customer problems — Girish opens up like never before. He talks about career lessons, handling challenges, building for Gen Z, and why he believes India is ready to lead the AI era.

🔍 Topics Covered in This Episode:
 • Freshworks and Riding the Wave
 • The Rise of AI – A Monster Wave
 • Adapting Freshworks to the AI Era
 • Why AI Is a Disruptive Monster
 • Is SaaS Dead? The Shift to AI with Freddy
 • How AI Enhances SaaS
 • Layoffs & AI’s Human Impact
 • India’s Transition: Services to Products
 • The Real Product Revolution
 • Why India’s Moment is Now

snippet.title: KINGDOM Release Date Promo - TAMIL | Vijay Deverakonda | Anirudh | Naga Vamsi | Gowtam Tinnanuri
snippet.description:
#KINGDOM~ Starring Vijay Deverakonda in Lead Role. Directed by Gowtam Tinnanuri. Music by Anirudh Ravichander. Editing by Navin Nooli. Produced by Naga Vamsi S & Sai Soujanya Under Sithara Entertainments & Fortune 4 Cinemas Banner. Presented by Srikara Studios.

#Kingdom will roar in theatres Worldwide on July 31st! 👊🏾

Starring: Vijay Deverakonda, Satyadev, Bhagyashri Borse and Others

Crew Details:

Written & Directed By: Gowtam Tinnanuri 
Produced By: Naga Vamsi S – Sai Soujanya 
Music Composed By: Anirudh Ravichander
Cinematography: Jomon T John ISC, Girish Gangadharan ISC
Editor: Navin Nooli
Production Designer: Avinash Kolla
Costume Designer: Neeraja Kona
Song Choreographer: Dar Gai, Vijay Binni
Action Choreographer’s: Yannick Ben, Chethan D’Souza, Real Satish
Colorist: Ranga (Prasad Studio)
Sound Design: Sync Cinema
VFX Supervisor:  Vasudeva Rao M 
Co – Director: Sri Vastav 
Production Team: Girish Dasika, Uma Mahesh Karumanchi 
Audio on Aditya Music

Chief Associate Director: Basheer
Associate Directors: B.V. Raveendra, Tirumala Reddy Akki, Muthayam Vijay Kumar, Mahesh Talluri, Geetha Sapuru & Nallandula Jagadeesh
Assistant Directors: Manoj Rishie, MS Vihari, Shrikaran Beecharaju, Akhil Raj & Parth Bane
Associate Editor’s: Srinu Bainaboyina & Vishnu Ramagiri
Assistant Editor’s: Srinivas Nadiminti & Thallapelli Pavan Gowd
Online Editor: Santosh Kiran

A Sithara Entertainments Production
in Association with Fortune Four Studios
Presented by Srikara Studios

Additional Rhythm Programmed by Shashank Vijay

snippet.title: Maharashtra के Bhiwandi में रिक्शावाले ने MNS वाले को पीट दिया I Shiv Sena MNS Mumbai- SN
snippet.description:
#breakingnews #hindinews  #Rajthackeray #MnsShivsena #mnsnews #mumbaimnsnews

MNS bhiwandi video Maharashtra news : महाराष्ट्र डायरीज में आज हम बात करेंगे
1 )  ठाणे जिले के भिवंडी इलाके में एक उत्तर भारतीय रिक्शा चालक और
मराठी युवक के बीच किराए को लेकर विवाद हुआ। यह विवाद बाद में इतना बढ़
गया कि नौबत मारपीट तक पहुंच गई। आरोप है कि इस विवाद के दौरान रिक्शा
चालक ने मराठी युवक की पिटाई कर दी। इस घटना की जानकारी मिलते ही मनसे
टीम एक्टिव हो गई। एमएनएस के भिवंडी अध्यक्ष मनोज गुलवी ने इस मामले में
हस्तक्षेप कर रिक्शा चालक को माफी मांगने पर मजबूर किया।
2 ) वहीं मराठी और हिंदी को लेकर चल रहे विवाद को देखते हुए महाराष्ट्र
नवनिर्माण सेना के अध्यक्ष राज ठाकरे ने अपने पार्टी के कार्यकर्ताओं ने
चुप रहने की नसीहत दे दी है.
3 ) IMD Rain Alert: महाराष्ट्र के नागपुर में  पिछले 48 घंटों से
मूसलाधार बारिश हो रही है। भारतीय मौसम विज्ञान विभाग (IMD) ने नागपुर
में भारी बारिश जारी रहने की संभावना जताई है। भारी बारिश की चेतावनी के
मद्देनजर नागपुर जिले के सभी स्कूल, कॉलेज और कोचिंग सेंटर 9 जुलाई 2025
को बंद रहेंगे। यह आदेश जिला कलेक्टर डॉ. विपिन इटनकर ने जारी किया है।
महाराष्ट्र के विदर्भ क्षेत्र में आज के लिए ऑरेंज अलर्ट जारी किया गया
है, जिसमें नागपुर सहित अमरावती, अकोला, चंद्रपुर और गढ़चिरौली जिलों में
भारी बारिश की चेतावनी जारी की गई है। नागपुर में मंगलवार सुबह 8:30 बजे
से बुधवार सुबह 5:30 बजे तक 172.2 मिमी बारिश दर्ज की गई है, जिससे शहर
के कई निचले इलाकों में जलभराव की स्थिति उत्पन्न हो गई है।
प्रादेशिक मौसम विभाग, नागपुर के अनुसार, पश्चिम बंगाल के पास बने निम्न
दबाव क्षेत्र के कारण विदर्भ का पूर्वी हिस्सा विशेष रूप से प्रभावित हुआ
है। नागपुर, अकोला, अमरावती और वर्धा में अत्यधिक बारिश हुई है।

snippet.title: Blessed With Baby Boy Allhamdullilah👶🏻❤️ | Adnaan 07
snippet.description:
Today, my life changed forever.
I became a father and Alhamdulillah, it’s a baby boy.

The moment I heard his first cry, something inside me shifted. A love I never knew existed was born. It’s hard to put into words what it feels like, but I tried capturing every moment, every emotion, and every heartbeat.

This video holds one of the most precious memories of my life. The arrival of my son. The nervousness, the joy, the tears, and the silent prayers.

Thank you for being a part of this journey. Your love and duas mean more than words can ever say.

This is the beginning of something truly beautiful. Do remember us in your prayers.✨

#FathersLove #BabyBoy #Adnaan07 #AdnaanShaikh

snippet.title: Renault Dacia Duster 2025 Drive Impressions | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Namaste. If the Ford Endeavour is the most anticipated SUV Indians are waiting for, it is the Duster that Renault fans are waiting for. Fortunately, the French have not left India like the Americans did, so we can say that Duster will come before Endeavour if the Almighty listens to our prayers. Here is a walkaround and drive Impression of the all-new Duster, which is already on sale in many markets outside India. 


Timestamps:
00:00 Introduction
01:29 Exteriors including Key fob, Wheels, Doors, Boot, Headlights, ADAS, etc
09:00 Engine Bay
09:40 Interiors including MID, Infotainment, Seats, Space etc
23:08 Rear seat Space and Amenities
25:05 Drive Impressions Including Ride, Handling, Engine, Gearbox, braking and Fuel Economy
33:56 Conclusion


Transparency Note:
We sourced the vehicle used for this video from a source outside the manufacturer’s control. No help whatsoever was taken from a manufacturer unless otherwise mentioned. Mr Gagan Choudhary or GaadiFy bear any charges incurred in travel, refuelling, Toll, parking, logistics, permits, etc. You can also give us a vehicle you have for shoot/review purposes and help us be free and fearlessly honest. Consumer interest is our top priority.

This disclaimer is voluntary and posted to maintain transparency.

snippet.description:
रॉय, मानव, आदित्य और बोमन नाम के चार आलसी दोस्त गोवा में छिपे खजाने को खोजने के लिए दौड़ लगाते हैं। हालाँकि, इंस्पेक्टर कबीर जल्द ही उनकी योजना के बारे में जान जाते हैं और अपनी राह पर निकल पड़ते हैं।

Four lazy friends named Roy, Manav, Aditya and Boman venture out on a race to find a hidden treasure in Goa. However, Inspector Kabir soon learns about their plan and sets out on their trail.

Movie Name - Dhamaal (2007) धमाल 
Star Cast - Arshad Warsi, Jaaved Jaffrey, Sanjay Dutt, Riteish Deshmukh, Ashish Chaudhary, Prem Chopra, Sanjay Mishra, Asrani, Vijay Raaz
Director - Indra Kumar

#dhammal #comedymovie #comedy 

Subscribe To Shemaroo Movie in Parts: https://www.youtube.com/user/shemaroopremiumfilms?sub_confirmation=1

Movie Name - Dhamaal (2007) 
Cast :  Sanjay Dutt, Arshad Warsi, Riteish Deshmukh, Arshad Warsi, Javed Jaffrey
Director : Indra Kumar

Dhamaal is about four friends afflicted by the get rich quick virus. Their fortunes take a turn after they accidentally bump into a victim who tells them about a hidden treasure who tells them about a hidden treasure in Goa including 10 crore rupees. The group race toward Goa in Contractors stolen car little knowing that their plans will soon be foiled albeit hilariously by Police Inspector Kabir Nayak - Sanjay Dutt. 

#SanjayDutt #ArshadWarsi #RiteishDeshmukh

मूवी का नाम - धमाल (2007)

snippet.description:
જિગ્નેશ બારોટના સુપરહિટ ગીત "કુદરત" નો નવો અંદાજ! હવે સાંભળો કુદરત 2.0 કાજલ મહેરીયા ની મીઠી અવાજમાં માત્ર @SaregamaGujarati પર! ❤️🎶

Lyrics:
હો  દિલ નું કેઉ માનું તો દુનિયા નડે છે 
હો  દિલ નું કેઉ માનુતો દુનિયા નડે છે
લોહી ના આંસુ  મારી આંખો રડે છે ...(.2.)
 તું મને ના ..મળી.. હું તને ના મળ્યો 
 તને મને જુદા કરી કુદરત રડ્યો....
 હો દિલ નું કેઉ માનુતો દુનિયા નડે છે
  લોહી ના આંસુ  મારી આંખો રડે છે ...
  હો લઈ જા ને યાદ મારી હાચવીને રાખજે
  મારી મોહોબત ને હમભાળી રાખજે 
  અરે તારો વિશ્વાસ કર્યો હદ થી વધારે ..
   કુદરત જાણે હવે મળશું પાછા ક્યારે....
   હું તારી યાદ મા રોઝ મરતો રહું
   તને યાદ કરી  જાન જીવતો રહું
   હો  દિલ નું કેઉ માનુ તો દુનિયા નડે છે 
   લોહી ના આંસુ આખો રડે છે
   ઓ ફૂલ થી સજેલો મારો બાગ કરમાંણો.....(2)
   તારા રે  કારણે મારો પ્રેમ વગોવાણો
   રોજ તને યાદ કરી રાત વીતી જાશે.... 
   તારી યાદો માં મારી જિંદગી પુરી થાશે 
   તું મને ના મળી  હું તને ના મળ્યો
   તને મને જુદા કરી કુદરત રડ્યો
   કાજલ ના  દિલ નું કેઉ માનું તો દુનિયા નડે છે
   લોહીના આસુ  મારી  આખો રડે છે
